## 2️⃣ Header patches – copy‑&‑paste

### 2.1. Add missing includes & Qt meta‑type registration

```cpp
#pragma once

#include <QString>
#include <QStringList>        // <-- needed for BehaviorPatch
#include <QObject>
#include <QJsonObject>
#include <QJsonArray>
#include <QDateTime>
#include <QMutex>
#include <QMetaType>          // <-- for Q_DECLARE_METATYPE
#include <vector>
